🚨TRANSPARENT POST🚨
💌 TO WHOMEVER NEEDS TO HEAR THIS 🤟🏾

💯 The struggle is real… sometimes getting through the day is a major accomplishment. We are living in critical times, hard to deal with 2 Timothy 3:1. This world can have a death grip on our estimation of ourselves… we often judge ourselves mirrors reflecting others, their accomplishments, achievements, successes, situation, status… whatever! It can easily make you feel small… HOWEVER!!! Rest assured that you are not the product of anything you have no control over… CHOOSE TO SEE LIGHT, however small it may appear…. Go toward that light…. The darkness will not last forever… hold onto the light! REMEMBER TO SATISFY YOUR SPIRITUAL NEED! MATTHEW 5:3. DRAW CLOSE TO GOD! JAMES 4:8. SURROUND YOURSELF WITH THOSE WHO WILL BRING THE BEST OUT OF YOU… STAY AWAY FROM NEGATIVE INFLUENCES. REMEMBER TO BE THANKFUL! 

With love… AUNDIE 🤟🏾🤟🏾🤟🏾🤟🏾🤟🏾

#thejourney #mentalhealthawareness #yahnhunterjnr #drumsolo #lovelife #inspiration #positivity #mybrotherskeeper

🧩WORLD AUTISM AWARENESS DAY!!!!! 

We have the grand privilege of raising a very beautiful, special, kind, loving, energetic, charismatic girly @ariah_l_simons. She is extremely smart and talented. She comes with some amazing features, the ability to hyper focus and she achieves everything she puts her mind to! 

It took a while to take her “training wheels” off only to realize she was part of a very special group of people. A people who are all individually and the are on quite an extensive spectrum of possibilities and challenges. @andrealsimons thank you so much for your persistence and determination to get this bumblebee support and really helping all of us to have a better understanding of how to support this beautiful creature. What the future holds for her??? Who knows, but it will be EXTREMELY BRIGHT! 
WE Love you Bumblebee! 

To all of those out there in the spectrum PEACE & LOVE WE WISH TO YOU ALL!!!!

#autism #autismawareness #autismacceptance
